text: RocketNews nominated for a Webby Award About Us: Rocketnews is an aggregator of the top online news articles and stories from around the globe. Addition news feed providers included online media suppliers, local and regional publications, industry journals, companies, governments, universities, PR companies, official organizations, associations, shopping guides and weblogs.
